data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN AT 2.875% FIXED FOR 30 YEARS, subject to lender approval.  Great opportunity!!!!!!Turnkey 4bdr 3bth home with LARGE POOL SIZED LOT, RV PARKING, and PAID OFF SOLAR.  Welcome home!  Here is your chance to own a 2020 built home with one of the largest lots in the beautiful Olivewood Community.  The sellers have upgraded all the flooring in the wet areas and kitchen to vinyl planks, the sellers had the builder install more recessed lighting downstairs, upgrade the cabinets in the kitchen, and granite counter tops throughout.  As you enter the home there is an oversized secondary bedroom to the right of the entry next to a full bathroom.  You have two storage closets in the hallway for your coats and Knick knacks.  The kitchen welcomes you with a large island, high ceilings, custom upgraded cabinetry, granite counter tops, and it opens up to the dining room and great room.  There is plenty of natural light to brighten the downstairs living area.  Upstairs you will find the primary suite, primary bathroom, 2 secondary bedrooms, the full bathroom, and the laundry room.  The primary suite is very ample in size, has carpet flooring, and an upgraded ceiling fan.  The primary restroom has dual sinks, a vanity area, a walk in shower, and a generously sized walk in closet.  The two secondary bedrooms have ceiling fans, carpet flooring, good sized closets, and ample space.  The backyard is a blank canvas waiting for its new owner to put their magic touch.  There is RV parking on the left hand side, a dog run on the right hand side, and space to possibly accommodate your new pool, spa, and bbq island.  Stop by today to view this beautiful home.
